title: Back In The Studio + Starting The New Year
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 1/3/2022. 

Rosenberg, Laura Stylez, and the crew are back in the studio for the first time in the New Year! Congratulations You Played Yourself is handed out to H&M and Antonio Brown (14), DJ John gives out prizes (21), and much more! 

Click here to learn about the Hot 97 - Securing the Future initiative.
